Another factor for sure is the broader context.

On a bigger picture, what we have admired in the last year is that people – I do not want to promote teleworking as a model but at least it shows that this form of work can be done at home and shifted towards an e-moderation structure.

Vis-a-vis our clubs, I believe that a blend between streaming and broadcasting on TV will be the way for us to grow in the near future.

On the growth trajectory of the brand, we need to position ourselves on the right channels. Last year, we launched the idea of our show and podcasts channel. ftb.wtf was actually at first intended to be a partner in sports and entertainment. We wanted to produce content for other brands as we positioned ourselves as influencers. This channel became the main working instrument for us at the beginning and it gave birth to the ftxf platform for sports.
